transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello, yes.
Executive: Hello. Haan, good afternoon, main Vineet baat kar raha hun IndiaMART head office se.
Customer: Haanji Vineet ji kaise hain aap?
Executive: Main theek hun mam aap kaise ho?
Customer: All good, all good.
Executive: Mam actually Ujjwal se na aapka discussion hua tha teen char din pehle. To uske baad aapke primary number pe isi number pe aapke WhatsApp pe feedback aaya hoga. Aapne usme not satisfied kiya hua hai.
Customer: Actually aapne ye Ujjwal ji meri Ujjwal ji se kafi time se baat nahi hui because I was out of station. Calls to aayi thi but I was out of station.
Executive: Ji, short se hui hogi fir mujhe lagta hai aapke yahan par. To uske baad uske baad na aapke WhatsApp main keh raha hun aapse nahi hui to aap out of station honge to kisi aur se to zarur hui thi on 24th of November ko.
Customer: 24th of November main bas check kara rahi hun kis se baat hui because koi hoti to mujhe detail mil jata.
Executive: Accha lekin usme feedback aapke hi mobile se aaya hua hai aur balki incoming aayi thi aapke phone se. Isi number se the.
Customer: Nahi nahi ek second ek second. 24th November ko mere se baat hui thi ya un kisi company number pe baat hui hai sir?
Executive: Nahi aap hi ke number se 908 last mein yahi ke number se.
Customer: Mere se baat hui thi?
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Ujjwal ji ki?
Executive: Haanji. 369 seconds ki baat hui hai.
Customer: Sir Ujjwal ji ki mere se koi bhi baat nahi hai agar aap mujhe number batayenge I can cross check.
Executive: Balki yahan pe aapki video meeting bhi hui hai 24 November ko. Met with client related.
Customer: Nahi sir meri koi meeting nahi hui hai. No meeting happened. I remember I checked my email. I didn't receive a notification.
Executive: 24 November ko kis se baat hui thi?
Customer: [inaudible] mang rahe the kya naam tha employee ka? [inaudible]
Customer: [inaudible] employee ka kaun aaya tha? [inaudible] mang rahe the kitna mera amount aur video meeting bhi hui hai aur wo puch rahe the ki kitna unka amount bacha hai ye sab discussion hua hai.
Customer: Kaunsi date ko hua tha sir aap date batayenge wapas mujhe?
Executive: 24th of November mam sham ko 5 baje ke aas pass.
Customer: I'll check with the team who followed up. Main aapko isse report karwati hun.
Executive: Theek hai mam till then na mam ek not satisfied ka ek ticket aaya hua hai. Aisa koi discussion to nahi hua kyuki agar aata to aapke pass number hai ye mera Ujjwal ka to aap mere ko.
Customer: Haan I have Ujjwal's number. Haan haan aisa kuch nahi hai main pehle check karti hun meeting kisne attend kari hai.
Executive: Bilkul mam main tab tak concern close kar raha hun mam ab jo feedback aayega usko please satisfied mark kijiyega aap.
Customer: Pehle main check kar leti hun meeting kisne join kari hai kya baat hui thi main aapko bhej deti hun.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai koi nahi aap call back kar lijiyega. Hai na? Theek hai sir.
Executive: Okay mam. Okay. Okay.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer denies having a meeting on November 24th.

- Customer received a 'not satisfied' feedback request.



Resolution:

- Executive will keep the ticket open until confirmation.

- Customer agreed to check meeting details and revert.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will check meeting details and revert.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- feedback, meeting, follow up, not satisfied
